title: So that IEM Match is even more evidence about how stagnant the SEA Competitive Region is...
body: Pathetic. I would be embarrassed if I was from that server. Utterly humiliating defeat. That was a slaughter.

replies.body:
SK surprised everyone with their vision. They seemed to ward way more than they do normally in an average LCS game.

SK v yFW was just as one sided as GE v C9. It is just that SK lacks the ability to push their advantage as hard as GE does.
C9 looked just as bad in their loss to be fair.
